story_description:

for timeless style. Made in a blend of cotton-elastane, using the proprietary ThermoVent technology,

title: Shadow Gray Slim Fit Mid-Rise Clean Look Stretchable Denim
story_description:
Story it's got a perfect Vintage hue and characteristics in the wash. it's so legit, it's hard to
tell (by looking) that it's not a well-loved cotton jean that's been worn hard for years. and for
those of you who have been asking for a zipper fly… this one's for you. FRENCH CROWN Jean is cut for

elevated finishes and differentiated modern details, and is made with Performance advanced stretch
technology for ultimate comfort and maximum mobility. With an exquisite hand-feel and beautiful
drape, you’ll want to wear them every day. Whether you wear them with a matching t-shirt or pair
them with your favorite Shirt, you’re sure to make a smart impression.
